			White ladder all covered with water has also always stumped. Last night I dreamed that I was singing the song and when I woke up I visualized the white ladder (height) covered in water. I thought of climate change and the melting of the ice caps. The last line before the chorus - I'll know my songs well before I start singing - to me refers to getting facts straight before shooting off at the mouth. <br />
Just a thought			<div class="sign">

